2025-09-10T09:21:39.3102720Z 4. Perform the basic installation of the Nix files daemon.
2025-09-10T09:21:39.3103092Z
2025-09-10T09:21:39.3103383Z 5. Configure your shell to import special Nix Profile files, so you
2025-09-10T09:21:39.3103913Z    can use Nix.
2025-09-10T09:21:39.3104098Z
2025-09-10T09:21:39.3104229Z 6. Start the Nix daemon.
